Commentary Text: Hasaranga to Markram, out Caught by Kohli!! Hasaranga strikes in his first over. A floated delivery around middle and leg, probably a googly, Markram goes down on his knee to play the slogsweep and hits this straight to Kohli at deep mid-wicket. VK makes no mistake and the leg spinner breaks the 50-run partnership. Hasn't been the easiest of wickets to bat on and Sunrisers have lost their third wicket. Markram c Kohli b Hasaranga 21(27) [4s-1 6s-1]

Commentary Text: Maxwell to Abhishek Sharma, out Williamson Run Out!! What an unfortunate start to SRH's innings. A short ball outside off and Abhishek Sharma punches it to Shahbaz Ahmed at cover. Calls for a run, and the fielder does well to score a direct-hit at the keeper's end with only one stump to aim at. Williamson's bat is on the line and the line belongs to the umpire. Sunrisers lose their captain on the first ball of the run chase. Williamson run out (Shahbaz Ahmed) 0(0)
